{"tid":2184060,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"（7月14自彈自唱）電台禁歌 麥潔文 - 夜夜痴纏","createTime":"2020-09-01T10:07:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T17:29:48.000Z","uid":18975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1a9760d39cfbbb4c8bb51fb93b8a4f5fc32589ab","tid":2184060,"uid":18975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T10:07:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9iCibnAX3Ro\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9iCibnAX3Ro&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYdRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=f70135a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9iCibnAX3Ro</a><br />\n<br />\n一直都好想唱呢首傳聞嘅禁歌<br />\n農曆7月14特別想送呢首歌比嗰班濫用權力、武力去打壓弱勢嘅人聽，希望佢哋一世都比魔鬼詛咒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以首歌有啲位我改咗幾隻字。<br />\n<br />\n作詞：林振強   作曲：顧嘉煇<br />\n矇矓晚空 雨霧瀰漫<br />\n夜已半躺窗紗間<br />\n在你臂彎裡 漫長夜晚<br />\n有我的一張笑顏<br />\n<br />\n祈求你可繼續留下<br />\n讓我愛多千幾番<br />\n但我知道 在晨霧裡<br />\n你將孤單 你將消失 像這一晚<br />\n<br />\n惟求你知 此刻太短<br />\n請將此身 盡舖以吻<br />\n惟求你知 怨是難斷<br />\n橫跨一生怨恨<br />\n<br />\n如能再生於此世間<br />\n願再不須孤單<br />\n若我他生又重遇你<br />\n你可不可與我一起度每一晚"},{"pid":"5d364d1c73630c873b7594da689945515e6ed0c7","tid":2184060,"uid":18975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T12:03:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"747ff29a92ce5fdb659f779e1863d23ba116958b","tid":2184060,"uid":18975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T13:49:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09184b28eaa565bfecea0b8a856aba5e6f3ea69d","tid":2184060,"uid":18975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T14:15:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67a07c59490bb30a27bcdce667d1486ef41cab59","tid":2184060,"uid":88855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T09:52:15.000Z","msg":"巴打唱得幾好聽 想問你係用乜嘢software去錄同執啲effect"},{"pid":"9091d2a0b25d